01:25.800 --> 01:29.700
No, Mom. Look at me. I'm huge,
and I'm gonna get more huge.

01:29.700 --> 01:31.000
It's OK, Amy. 

01:31.000 --> 01:35.000
Your dad loves you, and so
do I, and so does your sister.

01:36.600 --> 01:38.400
You don't have to go away.

01:38.400 --> 01:40.800
I don't mind asking your grandmother
if you can stay with her.

01:40.800 --> 01:43.100
I don't even mind telling her
why you want to stay with her,

01:43.100 --> 01:45.800
but you don't have to stay with her.

01:45.800 --> 01:46.900
You can stay here.

01:46.900 --> 01:49.300
Mom... let me go.

01:49.300 --> 01:51.500
You said I could go.
You promised me.

01:51.500 --> 01:55.500
I know, Amy, but I can't imagine
not seeing you every day,

01:55.500 --> 01:57.000
being with you through all this.

01:57.000 --> 01:58.800
I don't want you
to see me like this.

01:58.900 --> 02:00.200
I don't want anyone
to see me like this.

02:00.200 --> 02:02.800
I just....I wanna do this all alone.

02:02.800 --> 02:05.000
But you're not alone.

02:05.300 --> 02:06.600
We're alone.

02:07.000 --> 02:08.000
Finally.

02:08.400 --> 02:11.000
Mom's been waiting for you.
You're gonna be late for school.

02:11.000 --> 02:13.500
Yeah, well, at least I'm not
gonna be late for my period.

02:13.500 --> 02:15.500
Ashley, apologize.

02:15.500 --> 02:18.000
Fine. I apologize.

02:18.600 --> 02:21.700
But you know she's pregnant. I don't
see why some good can't come of it.

02:21.800 --> 02:24.000
Why can't you make Dad come
home and have him help?

02:24.000 --> 02:26.900
I'm not even gonna be here, Ashley.

02:29.600 --> 02:31.000
I thought you two
were getting along.

02:31.000 --> 02:32.700
I thought you and Dad
were getting along.

02:32.700 --> 02:33.900
We're talking about Amy.

02:33.900 --> 02:36.000
That's all we ever do
is talk about Amy.

02:36.000 --> 02:37.700
Can't we talk about Dad for once?

02:37.700 --> 02:39.800
Your dad is the one
who decided to leave.

02:39.800 --> 02:42.500
Dad decided to leave.
Amy decided to leave.

02:42.500 --> 02:44.500
Maybe I'll decide to leave.

