before you leave town.

31:18.714 --> 31:21.324
Are you leaving?
That's the rumor around school.

31:21.324 --> 31:22.808
Maybe. 

31:23.556 --> 31:26.227
Did you say you actually
talked to my dad earlier?

31:26.227 --> 31:30.075
