I don't think I can keep.

31:30.075 --> 31:31.049
Like?

31:31.049 --> 31:33.889
Like I think I do wanna
be involved.

31:33.889 --> 31:35.177
Seriously?

31:35.177 --> 31:36.217
Involved?

31:36.217 --> 31:37.792
I'm the father of this child,

31:37.792 --> 31:40.508
and I think I should have
some say in what happens here.

31:41.874 --> 31:45.742
Just call me when I can come over
and talk to you, OK?

31:53.854 --> 31:56.055
OK, now I see how it happened.

31:58.614 --> 32:00.646
She's beautiful,
don't you think?

32:05.326 --> 32:08.232
I know we're a little young,

32:08.232 --> 32:12.376
and... she's
a little pregnant...

32:13.871 --> 32:17.270
...but I'm really in love,

32:18.334 --> 32:20.549
and I don't think
she understands that.

32:21.590 --> 32:23.216
If she did, I don't think she'd 

32:23.604 --> 32:26.198
be running off
to her grandmother's house.

32:26.650 --> 32:30.709
This is the woman I wanna spend
the rest of my life with.

32:32.645 --> 32:35.316
She says she feels
the same way about me, but...

32:37.954 --> 32:39.169
I don't know.

32:40.005 --> 32:43.746
Of course, it's complicated,
but life is complicated.

32:44.079 --> 32:47.753
Heh. I sound like Dad,
don't I?

32:48.426 --> 32:51.745
Except Dad would add,
"Sausage is complicated."

32:52.464 --> 32:53.843
Probably. 

32:55.161 --> 32:56.977
That's not her,
you know.

32:57.495 --> 32:58.634
It's her.

32:59.166 --> 33:02.888
Nah, that's the container that holds
 the container that used to be her.

33:04.351 --> 33:08.082
Is this the first time you've come to see her
since we said goodbye to her?

33:08.222 --> 33:11.332
It is, yeah.
I don't like coming here.

33:11.365 --> 33:13.488
But I didn't come for her,
I came for you.

33:13.806 --> 33:17.279
Why do you come here every year
on the anniversary of her death?

33:17.293 --> 33:19.972
Why do you do this
to yourself every year?

33:19.972 --> 33:22.195
'Cause every day
would be too often.

33:22.195 --> 33:24.527
Life is for the living, son.

33:24.527 --> 33:27.121
You can talk to the deceased
but not the living?

33:27.121 --> 33:28.521
