33:28.901 --> 33:31.112
If Amy's leaving
and going to her grandma's,

33:31.112 --> 33:32.481
then that's what's happening.

33:32.976 --> 33:35.226
Do you won't be together
for the rest of your lives.

33:35.226 --> 33:37.915
