George.

39:15.959 --> 39:18.905
You know, maybe it
 really is time I come home.

39:18.905 --> 39:20.256
Or not.

39:20.256 --> 39:21.546
We got one daughter
who's pregnant

39:21.546 --> 39:22.816
and another one
who's skipping school.

39:22.816 --> 39:23.712
Your point being?

39:23.713 --> 39:25.888
Point being is you
need me around here

39:25.888 --> 39:27.583
Correct me if I'm wrong,

39:27.584 --> 39:30.601
but weren't you living here
when Amy got pregnant?

39:30.822 --> 39:34.086
And I'm pretty sure you were here this
 morning when Ashley skipped school.

39:34.086 --> 39:36.789
Come on. I know
we have problems,

39:36.789 --> 39:38.684
but we're not gonna fix our marriage
with me outta the house.

39:38.684 --> 39:41.951
It took me a few weeks to realize it,
 but, hey, at least I realized it.

39:41.951 --> 39:43.750
I'm not so sure I wanna fix
our marriage.

39:43.750 --> 39:46.808
Did you tell Mimsy you and I are living apart?
Does your mother know?

39:46.808 --> 39:48.271
She doesn't need
to know that.

39:48.271 --> 39:50.794
I can't imagine
she'd be too happy about it.

39:51.178 --> 39:54.070
She likes me...
better than you, even.

39:54.070 --> 39:56.248
Yeah, she likes everyone
better than me.

39:58.384 --> 40:00.277
So... Amy?

40:00.836 --> 40:03.773
She can stay there. I got
a referral for a doctor,

40:03.773 --> 40:06.232
and I met her,
she seems very nice.

40:06.279 --> 40:08.860
She's getting Amy into a group
with other teen mothers.

40:08.860 --> 40:11.536
I don't want my daughter
associating with girls like that.

40:11.831 --> 40:13.548
Come on, I wanna come home.

40:13.548 --> 40:15.143
Where are you staying now?

40:15.631 --> 40:17.129
You know, here and there.

40:17.452 --> 40:21.178
I checked our credit-card account,
 and there aren't any hotel bills on there.

40:22.790 --> 40:24.641
You're not staying
at the store, are you?

40:24.641 --> 40:26.001
Well, I'm...

40:26.725 --> 40:28.540
Yeah, I didn't think so.

40:29.043 --> 40:31.903
So why don't you slither
on back down the driveway,

40:31.903 --> 40:33.914
back to wherever it is
that you are staying?

40:35.009 --> 40:35.821
