40:37.157 --> 40:40.132
-I told him to leave her alone.
-I told her to talk to him.

40:40.132 --> 40:41.571
We'll see who's right
about this.

40:41.571 --> 40:44.315
Call me when you need my help,
'cause you're gonna need my help.

40:44.315 --> 40:46.366
-Good night, George.
-Good night, Anne.

40:48.716 --> 40:50.063
This is my house, too,you know.

40:50.063 --> 40:51.247
Yeah, I know.

40:59.218 --> 41:00.797
I'm not saying
I'm against adoption.

41:00.797 --> 41:03.295
