of speaking for myself!

41:17.334 --> 41:18.437
Since when?

41:18.437 --> 41:20.269
Since I got pregnant!

41:20.269 --> 41:21.692
That's when.

41:21.959 --> 41:24.088
Since I discovered I'm going
to have to take charge

41:24.088 --> 41:26.039
of another human being's life.

41:26.798 --> 41:28.638
I might as well start
with my own.

41:28.639 --> 41:29.983
OK, OK.

41:29.983 --> 41:32.022
But I'd like to know where you are
and what's going on,

41:32.022 --> 41:33.638
if you don't mind.

41:33.639 --> 41:35.121
Maybe I do mind.

41:35.704 --> 41:39.705
I'll think about what you said,
and I'll call you.

41:40.072 --> 41:42.814
When? When are you
gonna call me?

41:42.814 --> 41:44.103
