41:44.103 --> 41:46.302
OK, I'll take that.
Thanks.

41:46.303 --> 41:47.522
You're welcome.

41:48.202 --> 41:49.270
Now go home.

41:51.193 --> 41:53.316
Do you wanna exchange
phone numbers?

41:53.316 --> 41:58.148
No. I'm pretty sure I can find your number
 if and when I want to call you.

41:59.480 --> 42:00.436
Good night.

42:00.436 --> 42:01.506
Good night.

42:10.039 --> 42:10.642
What?

42:10.642 --> 42:13.250
