I hope you don't mind.

42:13.250 --> 42:15.197
I was coming up the walk,
and I saw your dad pull up,

42:15.197 --> 42:18.599
and I knew Ricky was inside,
so... I got stuck.

42:19.108 --> 42:20.463
I don't mind.

42:22.607 --> 42:24.471
I don't mind at all.

42:25.744 --> 42:28.086
No, no, no. Stay.

42:29.149 --> 42:32.609
That bump - that's not me.

42:33.672 --> 42:35.455
It's the baby.

42:36.052 --> 42:37.826
Yeah, I thought so.

